### User Stories
	(% indicate MVP deliverables, everything else are nice-to-haves)
* % C - user can login through authenticated account
* % user can logout
* % R - user can create a post with text and an image
* % U - user can update their own posts
* % D - user can delete their own posts
* user can comment on other user posts
* user can rate based on 5 star rating other user posts
* user can view all of just their own posts
* user can block viewing specific user posts from main view, when viewing all posts
